Signup confirmation
===============================================
You receive this e-mail because you or someone else 
have signed up account on calories.today.

To complete registration click this link: 
https://calories.today/confirm-account/<%= @user.signup_confirmation_token %>



If you didn't make this request, click here:
https://calories.today/report-fraudulent-account/<%= @user.signup_confirmation_token %>
It will result in automatic account disabling
and will remove your e-mail from our database 
so you will be able to register in future if you decide to.

